<style>
.testdiv { font-family: monospace; width: 6.340282366920938463463374607431768211456ch; padding: 0px; margin: 1px; border: 1px solid silver; }
.test { word-break: break-all; }
</style>
<div>Test passes if the two boxes are the same.</div>
<div class="testdiv"><style>aaaaaaa</style><span class="test">bbb</span></div>
